item.title: CVE-2023-32986|2024-08-02T15:32:46.615Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20file%20parameter%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins File Parameter Plugin 285.v757c5b_67a_c25 and earlier does not restrict the name (and resulting uploaded file name) of Stashed File Parameters, allowing attackers with Item/Configure permission to create or replace arbitrary files on the Jenkins controller file system with attacker-specified content.
